@NODE Introduzione "INTRODUCTION"
    All the persons that, having a modem, frequently upload and download
    files with a BBS or (Aminet) need this program. Infact, it allow to keep the accounts
    of upload-download files.
    This program allow to:

    1 - Be able to plan in advance operations on-line.
    2 - To avoid to receive and send more times the same program to the
        same BBS.
    3 - Be able to see data about files sent and files received
        and about connections made.


    @{"INDEX" link Main}
@ENDNODE 

@NODE Autore "AUTHOR"
    My name is Stefano Nardi, I live in Milan and I am an user of Amiga.
    I have developed this program on my Amiga 1200 with 6MB of RAM using
    SAS/C 6.51 and GoldEd.

    My address is:

